><br><br></p></div>]]>;</content:encoded></item><item><title>哪位音乐高管最具影响力？立即投票</title><link/>https://www.billboard.com/business/business-news/music-executives-compete-vote-power-players-choice-award-1235516644/<dc:creator><![CDATA[Colin Stutz]]></dc:creator><pubDate> Wed, 03 Jan 2024 04:15:08 +0000</pubDate> <category><![CDATA[Business]]></category><category><![CDATA[Business News]]></category><category><![CDATA[billboard pro]]></category><category><![CDATA[Power 100]]></category><category><![CDATA[power players]]></category><category><![CDATA[Power Players&#039; Choice Awards]]></category><guid ispermalink="false"> https://www.billboard.com/?p=1235516644 </guid><description><![CDATA[Finalist voting is now open for Billboard’s peer-voted Power Players' Choice Award.]]></description><content:encoded><![CDATA[<!-- do not apply CSS styles to this element! --><div class="pmc-paywall"><p
		class="paragraph larva // lrv-u-margin-lr-auto  lrv-a-font-body-m   "
> <em>《告示牌</em>》权力玩家选择奖的决赛入围投票正在进行中，该奖项旨在表彰同行认为在过去一年中对整个业务产生最大影响的高管。 </p><div class="injected-related-story // lrv-u-margin-tb-2 lrv-u-border-t-1 lrv-u-border-b-1 lrv-u-padding-t-050 lrv-u-padding-b-075 lrv-u-border-color-grey" ><div class="a-heading-border a-heading-border-background-color-grey a-heading-border-height-075 lrv-u-margin-b-075 lrv-u-margin-b-050@mobile-max"><h3 id="title-of-a-story" class="c-title  lrv-u-color-brand-primary a-font-primary-bold-s lrv-u-text-transform-uppercase lrv-u-padding-r-1 a-article-related-module-title a-article-related-module-title--color-brand-primary">有关的</h3></div><div class="o-card lrv-u-flex"><div class="c-lazy-image  lrv-u-height-100p"><div class="a-crop-3x2 a-crop-1x1@mobile-max lrv-u-height-100p"><img class="c-lazy-image__img lrv-u-background-color-grey-lightest lrv-u-width-100p lrv-u-display-block lrv-u-height-auto" src="https://www.billboard.com/wp-content/themes/vip/pmc-billboard-2021/assets/public/lazyload-fallback.gif" data-lazy-src="https://www.billboard.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/players-top-business-managers-billboard-2023-bb15-blas-bulnes-2-pro-1260.jpg?w=237&#038;h=147&#038;crop=1" alt="球员、顶级业务经理，艾德·希兰" data-lazy-srcset="" data-lazy-sizes="" height="" width=""></div></div></div><div class="o-card__content lrv-u-flex lrv-u-flex-direction-column lrv-u-justify-content-center lrv-u-padding-lr-1 lrv-u-padding-lr-075@mobile-max"><div class="o_category "></div><div class="c_title "><h3 id="title-of-a-story" class="c-title  a-font-primary-medium-m lrv-u-padding-b-050 u-letter-spacing-0028@mobile-max"> Billboard 2023 年度最佳商业经理人揭晓</h3></div><time class="c-timestamp  a-font-primary-medium-xxs lrv-u-color-brand-primary lrv-u-order-100" datetime="00:00-YY-DD-MM"> 2024年1月2日</time></div></div></div><p
		class="paragraph larva // lrv-u-margin-lr-auto  lrv-a-font-body-m   "
> <a  href="https://www.billboard.com/pro/billboard-power-players-choice-award-vote-music-executives"  >投票对所有<em>Billboard Pro</em>会员（包括现有会员和新会员）开放</a>，每轮每位会员一票。该奖项将与<em>Billboard</em>年度 Power 100 音乐行业最具影响力高管排名一起评选，该排名将于 2 月份公布。</p><p
		class="paragraph larva // lrv-u-margin-lr-auto  lrv-a-font-body-m   "
>经过公开征集提名和前 20 轮半决赛投票后，五名决赛入围者现在将参加第三轮投票，选出获胜者。投票于美国东部时间 1 月 14 日晚上 11:59 结束。</p><p
		class="paragraph larva // lrv-u-margin-lr-auto  lrv-a-font-body-m   "
> <em>Billboard</em>去年 1 月推出了<a  href="https://www.billboard.com/pro/brandon-silverstein-2023-billboard-power-players-choice-award/"  >首个 Power 100 玩家选择奖</a>，随后是 6 月结束的<a  href="https://www.billboard.com/pro/morgan-wallen-manager-seth-england-country-power-players-award/"  >乡村音乐玩家选择奖</a>、8 月的<a  href="https://www.billboard.com/pro/quality-control-pierre-thomas-rb-hip-hop-power-players-award/"  >R&amp;B/Hip-Hop 玩家选择奖</a>和<a  href="https://www.billboard.com/pro/maluma-manager-walter-kolm-latin-power-players-choice-award/"  >拉丁音乐玩家选择奖</a>九月份<a  href="https://www.billboard.com/pro/maluma-manager-walter-kolm-latin-power-players-choice-award/"  >颁奖</a>。 2024 年，同行投票奖项将扩大到涵盖国际实力人物和顶级音乐律师。</p><p
		class="paragraph larva // lrv-u-margin-lr-auto  lrv-a-font-body-m   "
>五名决赛入围者是：</p><div class="container // lrv-u-margin-lr-auto lrv-a-font-body-m   "><ul><li> <strong>Omar Al-joulani</strong> （Live Nation 音乐会巡回演出主席）</li><li><strong>乔迪·格尔森</strong>（环球音乐出版集团董事长/首席执行官）</li><li><strong>卢西恩·格兰奇</strong>（环球音乐集团董事长/首席执行官）</li><li> <strong>Mike Knobloch</strong> （NBC环球音乐与出版总裁）</li><li> <strong>Jesús López</strong> （环球音乐拉丁美洲和伊比利亚半岛董事长/首席执行官）</li></ul></div><p
		class="paragraph larva // lrv-u-margin-lr-auto  lrv-a-font-body-m   "
> <a  href="https://www.billboard.com/pro/billboard-power-players-choice-award-vote-music-executives"  >立即投票</a>，如果您还不是<em>Billboard Pro</em>的会员，<a  href="https://www.billboard.com/subscribe/"  >请在此处加入</a>。</p></div> ]]>;</content:encoded></item><item><title> Billboard 的强力玩家选择奖：投票选出音乐界最具影响力的执行官（入围者）</title><link/> https://www.billboard.com/pro/billboard-power-players-choice-award-vote-music-executives/<dc:creator><![CDATA[Colin Stutz]]></dc:creator><pubDate> Wed, 03 Jan 2024 04:10:58 +0000</pubDate> <category><![CDATA[Business]]></category><category><![CDATA[Business News]]></category><category><![CDATA[billboard pro]]></category><category><![CDATA[Power 100]]></category><category><![CDATA[power players]]></category><category><![CDATA[Power Players&#039; Choice Awards]]></category><guid ispermalink="false"> https://www.billboard.com/?post_type=billboard_pro_post&amp;p=1235516643 </guid><description><![CDATA[The peer-voted award allows the music business to participate in Billboard's Power 100 ranking of the industry's most influential executives.]]></description><content:encoded><![CDATA[<!-- do not apply CSS styles to this element! --><div class="pmc-paywall"><p
